										</a>
																		<p class="line-height-md color-carbon-40 margin-0 padding-0 p-sm">So big it has to fold origami-style to fit in the rocket and will unfold like a “Transformer” in space.</p>
									<div class="meet-the-icons">
																																							</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
