									</a>
																<div class="hds-meet-the-content">
									 
										<a href="https://science.nasa.gov/mission/webb/faqs-full/" target="_self"  class="display-block margin-bottom-1">
											<h3 class="heading-18 color-spacesuit-white link-underline-dashed-light border-carbon-30 margin-0 display-inline-block">1.5 Million km</h3>
										</a>
																		<p class="line-height-md color-carbon-40 margin-0 padding-0 p-sm">Webb orbits the Sun 1.5 million kilometers from the Earth. (Hubble orbits 560 kilometers above the Earth.)</p>
									<div class="meet-the-icons">
																																							</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
											<div class="hds-meet-the-card padding-right-7">
							<div class="hds-meet-the-inner display-flex">
								 
