									</a>
																<div class="hds-meet-the-content">
									 
										<a href="https://science.nasa.gov/mission/webb/faqs-full/" target="_self"  class="display-block margin-bottom-1">
											<h3 class="heading-18 color-spacesuit-white link-underline-dashed-light border-carbon-30 margin-0 display-inline-block">SPF 1 Million</h3>
										</a>
																		<p class="line-height-md color-carbon-40 margin-0 padding-0 p-sm">Webb has a 5-layer sunshield that protects the telescope from the infrared radiation of the Sun, Earth, and Moon; like having sun protection of SPF 1 million.</p>
