						<h2 class="display-60 color-spacesuit-white-important">NASA’s Webb Examines Cranium Nebula</h2>
					</div>
					<p class="p-lg color-spacesuit-white-important">Two heads are better than one in the latest images from NASA’s James Webb Space Telescope, which reveal new detail&hellip;</p>
					<a href="https://science.nasa.gov/missions/webb/nasas-webb-examines-cranium-nebula/" class="button-primary button-primary-md">
						<span class="section-heading-md color-spacesuit-white-important">Read the Story</span>
