<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Featured Webb Award</h2>



<p></p>


<div id="" class="hds-featured-image color-mode-light hds-color-mode-light hds-module hds-module-full alignfull wp-block-nasa-blocks-featured-image">
	<div class="grid-container grid-container-block padding-y-9 padding-x-3">
		<div class="grid-row">
			<div class="grid-col-12 desktop:grid-col-4 desktop:padding-right-5 margin-bottom-6 desktop:margin-bottom-0">
				<div class="margin-bottom-10 display-none tablet:display-block desktop:display-block">
					<h3 class="label">Jan 7, 2026</h3>
					<h2 class="display-41 margin-0">Webb Receives the SPIE 2026 George W. Goddard Award in Space and Airborne Optics</h2>
				</div>
				<p class="heading-22 margin-bottom-2">Awarded to Lee Feinberg, recognizing outstanding leadership through the design, integration, and delivery of optical systems that brought the objectives of the Webb and Hubble space telescopes into clear focus.</p>
				<p class="p-md"></p>
									</div>
			<div class="grid-col-12 desktop:grid-col-8 desktop:padding-left-5">
				<div class="margin-bottom-2 display-block tablet:display-none desktop:display-none">
